<SYNC Start=176305><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=176476><P Class=ENCC>
It's just weird what's happening<br>
with her and Ross.
<SYNC Start=178967><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=179179><P Class=ENCC>
