<SYNC Start=243135><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=243309><P Class=ENCC>
I know what we can do. We could set<br>
Ross and Rachel up on horrible dates..
<SYNC Start=246938><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=247113><P Class=ENCC>
so they'll realize<br>
how good they are together.
<SYNC Start=249638><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=249849><P Class=ENCC>
- That's a great plan.<br>
- Yeah.
<SYNC Start=251942><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=252151><P Class=ENCC>
You know what the best part of it is?<br>
I get to do my plan laugh.
<SYNC Start=256451><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=261494><P Class=ENCC>
Okay, shh! Not so loud.<br>
We don't want to wake up..
<SYNC Start=265954><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
