<SYNC Start=345433><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=345611><P Class=ENCC>
Thanks, you guys. Have fun.
<SYNC Start=347579><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=349949><P Class=ENCC>
Suddenly I wish I was reading<br>
